<label>
<input type="checkbox" checked="checked" id="download_regsheet_dci_details">
Include my DCI number and name </label>
(-&gt;
<a href="https://deckstats.net/settings/?lng=en" target="_blank">
Your Settings</a>)
</div>
<p>
<i>
Please note: This is not an official DCI service. So please always make extra sure that the sheet contains all the cards in your deck and fulfils all DCI requirements. If you notice anything wrong, please let us know! DCI is a trademark of of Wizards of the Coast LLC.
</i>
</p>
</div>

<div id="deck_tabs-tools">
<div class="section_header" id="deck_code_header">Embed Into Forums or Website</div>
<div class="inhalt2">
<div style="margin-bottom: 5px;">
For forums and blogs please select one of the BB-Code options. For websites and forums that support HTML (e.g. Wizards Community Forums) you can use the HTML options!	</div>
<div style="margin-top: 1em;">
<div>
<select name="code_type" id="code_type">
<option value="bb_deck">BB-Code with DECK tags (for MTG-Forum.de)</option>
<option value="bb_url">BB-Code with URL tags (recommended for most forums)</option>
<option value="markdown">Markdown List (for reddit)</option>
<option value="markdown_table">Markdown Table (for reddit)</option>
<option value="html_wide">HTML code for high table</option>
<option value="html_normal">HTML for wide table (recommended for Wizards Community)</option>
</select>
<select name="code_extended" id="code_extended">
<option value="0">Normal View</option>
<option value="1">Extended View (with mana symbols)</option>
</select>
<input class="button" type="submit" name="get_code" id="get_code" value="Generate Embed Code" />
</div>
<div>
<label id="code_html_nl_label">
<input name="code_html_nl" id="code_html_nl" type="checkbox" style="border: 0" />
Use linebreaks in HTML code (disable for Wizards Community) </label>
</div>
<script type="text/javascript">
			function generate_code_action(e) {
				e.preventDefault();

				document.location.href = 'https://deckstats.net/decks/48358/595557-mizzix-s-school-of-advanced-sp/en?get_code=1' +
					'&code_type=' + $('#code_type').val() +
					'&code_extended=' + $('#code_extended').val() +
					'&code_html_nl=' + ($('#code_html_nl').is(':checked')? 'on' : 'off');
			}

			$(function(){
				$('#get_code').click(generate_code_action);

				$('#code_type,#code_extended,#code_html_nl').change(function(e) {
					$('#code_result').hide();
				});
				$('#code_type').change(function(e) {
					if($(this).val().substr(0, 4) == 'html') {
						$('#code_html_nl_label').show();
					} else {
						$('#code_html_nl_label').hide();
					}
				});
				updateCodeType($('#code_type')[0]);
			});
		</script>

<div class="any_dialog" id="download_regsheet_dialog" title="Download Deck Sheet">
<p>
To play your deck at an official ("DCI-sanctioned") tournament you need a deck registration sheet. Here you can download such a sheet pre-filled with the cards in this deck!	</p>
<div style="margin-top: .5em">
<label for="download_regsheet_sort">Sort cards by:</label>
<select id="download_regsheet_sort" class="ui-corner-all">
<option value="name">Card Name</option>
<option value="amount">Amount</option>
<option value="type">Type</option>
<option value="none">do not sort</option>
</select>
</div>
<div style="margin-top: .5em">
<label>
<input type="checkbox" checked="checked" id="download_regsheet_dci_details">
Include my DCI number and name </label>
(-&gt;
<a href="https://deckstats.net/settings/?lng=en" target="_blank">
Your Settings</a>)
</div>
<p>
<i>
Please note: This is not an official DCI service. So please always make extra sure that the sheet contains all the cards in your deck and fulfils all DCI requirements. If you notice anything wrong, please let us know! DCI is a trademark of of Wizards of the Coast LLC.
</i>
</p>
</div>

<div class="section_header">Custom calculation</div>
<div class="inhalt2">
<div id="probcalc_input_manual">
If I play a card <input id="probcalc_input_manual_available" type="number" min="1" value="4"> times in my 100 card deck, how likely am I to draw it <select id="probcalc_input_manual_type"><option value="minimum">at least</option><option value="exact">exactly</option></select> <input id="probcalc_input_manual_wanted" type="number" min="1" value="2"> times? </div>
<div class="probcalc_input_buttons">
<button id="probcalc_input_calc_manual">Calculate</button>
</div>
</div>
</div>

<div id="deck_tabs-tools">
<div class="section_header" id="deck_code_header">Embed Into Forums or Website</div>
<div class="inhalt2">
<div style="margin-bottom: 5px;">
For forums and blogs please select one of the BB-Code options. For websites and forums that support HTML (e.g. Wizards Community Forums) you can use the HTML options!	</div>
<div style="margin-top: 1em;">
<div>
<select name="code_type" id="code_type">
<option value="bb_deck">BB-Code with DECK tags (for MTG-Forum.de)</option>
<option value="bb_url">BB-Code with URL tags (recommended for most forums)</option>
<option value="markdown">Markdown List (for reddit)</option>
<option value="markdown_table">Markdown Table (for reddit)</option>
<option value="html_wide">HTML code for high table</option>
<option value="html_normal">HTML for wide table (recommended for Wizards Community)</option>
</select>
<select name="code_extended" id="code_extended">
<option value="0">Normal View</option>
<option value="1">Extended View (with mana symbols)</option>
</select>
<input class="button" type="submit" name="get_code" id="get_code" value="Generate Embed Code" />
</div>
<div>
<label id="code_html_nl_label">
<input name="code_html_nl" id="code_html_nl" type="checkbox" style="border: 0" />
Use linebreaks in HTML code (disable for Wizards Community) </label>
</div>
<script type="text/javascript">
			function generate_code_action(e) {
				e.preventDefault();

				document.location.href = 'https://deckstats.net/decks/101422/1180806-swampqueen-lich-varina-command/en?get_code=1' +
					'&code_type=' + $('#code_type').val() +
					'&code_extended=' + $('#code_extended').val() +
					'&code_html_nl=' + ($('#code_html_nl').is(':checked')? 'on' : 'off');
			}

			$(function(){
				$('#get_code').click(generate_code_action);

				$('#code_type,#code_extended,#code_html_nl').change(function(e) {
					$('#code_result').hide();
				});
				$('#code_type').change(function(e) {
					if($(this).val().substr(0, 4) == 'html') {
						$('#code_html_nl_label').show();
					} else {
						$('#code_html_nl_label').hide();
					}
				});
				updateCodeType($('#code_type')[0]);
			});
		</script>
</div>
</div>

<div id="deck_tabs-edh">
<div class="inhalt2">
With this tool you can get recommendations for new cards to add to your EDH deck, based on which cards other players play with this Commander.	To make sure your deck is analyzed properly, please <b>flag your Commander in the deckbuilder</b> or put it in a separate section called "Commander"!</div>

<div id="deck_tabs-tools">
<div class="section_header" id="deck_code_header">Embed Into Forums or Website</div>
<div class="inhalt2">
<div style="margin-bottom: 5px;">
For forums and blogs please select one of the BB-Code options. For websites and forums that support HTML (e.g. Wizards Community Forums) you can use the HTML options!	</div>
<div style="margin-top: 1em;">
<div>
<select name="code_type" id="code_type">
<option value="bb_deck">BB-Code with DECK tags (for MTG-Forum.de)</option>
<option value="bb_url">BB-Code with URL tags (recommended for most forums)</option>
<option value="markdown">Markdown List (for reddit)</option>
<option value="markdown_table">Markdown Table (for reddit)</option>
<option value="html_wide">HTML code for high table</option>
<option value="html_normal">HTML for wide table (recommended for Wizards Community)</option>
</select>
<select name="code_extended" id="code_extended">
<option value="0">Normal View</option>
<option value="1">Extended View (with mana symbols)</option>
</select>
<input class="button" type="submit" name="get_code" id="get_code" value="Generate Embed Code" />
</div>
<div>
<label id="code_html_nl_label">
<input name="code_html_nl" id="code_html_nl" type="checkbox" style="border: 0" />
Use linebreaks in HTML code (disable for Wizards Community) </label>
</div>
<script type="text/javascript">
			function generate_code_action(e) {
				e.preventDefault();

				document.location.href = 'https://deckstats.net/decks/101422/920750-of-hereos-and-monsters-command/en?get_code=1' +
					'&code_type=' + $('#code_type').val() +
					'&code_extended=' + $('#code_extended').val() +
					'&code_html_nl=' + ($('#code_html_nl').is(':checked')? 'on' : 'off');
			}

			$(function(){
				$('#get_code').click(generate_code_action);

				$('#code_type,#code_extended,#code_html_nl').change(function(e) {
					$('#code_result').hide();
				});
				$('#code_type').change(function(e) {
					if($(this).val().substr(0, 4) == 'html') {
						$('#code_html_nl_label').show();
					} else {
						$('#code_html_nl_label').hide();
					}
				});
				updateCodeType($('#code_type')[0]);
			});
		</script>
</div>
</div>

<div class="section_header">Custom calculation</div>
<div class="inhalt2">
<div id="probcalc_input_manual">
If I play a card <input id="probcalc_input_manual_available" type="number" min="1" value="4"> times in my 100 card deck, how likely am I to draw it <select id="probcalc_input_manual_type"><option value="minimum">at least</option><option value="exact">exactly</option></select> <input id="probcalc_input_manual_wanted" type="number" min="1" value="2"> times? </div>

<div id="deck_tabs-tools">
<div class="section_header" id="deck_code_header">Embed Into Forums or Website</div>
<div class="inhalt2">
<div style="margin-bottom: 5px;">
For forums and blogs please select one of the BB-Code options. For websites and forums that support HTML (e.g. Wizards Community Forums) you can use the HTML options!	</div>
<div style="margin-top: 1em;">
<div>
<select name="code_type" id="code_type">
<option value="bb_deck">BB-Code with DECK tags (for MTG-Forum.de)</option>
<option value="bb_url">BB-Code with URL tags (recommended for most forums)</option>
<option value="markdown">Markdown List (for reddit)</option>
<option value="markdown_table">Markdown Table (for reddit)</option>
<option value="html_wide">HTML code for high table</option>
<option value="html_normal">HTML for wide table (recommended for Wizards Community)</option>
</select>
<select name="code_extended" id="code_extended">
<option value="0">Normal View</option>
<option value="1">Extended View (with mana symbols)</option>
</select>
<input class="button" type="submit" name="get_code" id="get_code" value="Generate Embed Code" />
</div>
<div>
<label id="code_html_nl_label">
<input name="code_html_nl" id="code_html_nl" type="checkbox" style="border: 0" />
Use linebreaks in HTML code (disable for Wizards Community) </label>
</div>
<script type="text/javascript">
			function generate_code_action(e) {
				e.preventDefault();

				document.location.href = 'https://deckstats.net/decks/90097/858006-inalla-edh-wizards/en?get_code=1' +
					'&code_type=' + $('#code_type').val() +
					'&code_extended=' + $('#code_extended').val() +
					'&code_html_nl=' + ($('#code_html_nl').is(':checked')? 'on' : 'off');
			}

			$(function(){
				$('#get_code').click(generate_code_action);

				$('#code_type,#code_extended,#code_html_nl').change(function(e) {
					$('#code_result').hide();
				});
				$('#code_type').change(function(e) {
					if($(this).val().substr(0, 4) == 'html') {
						$('#code_html_nl_label').show();
					} else {
						$('#code_html_nl_label').hide();
					}
				});
				updateCodeType($('#code_type')[0]);
			});
		</script>
</div>
</div>

<div id="deck_tabs-edh">
<div class="inhalt2">
With this tool you can get recommendations for new cards to add to your EDH deck, based on which cards other players play with this Commander.	To make sure your deck is analyzed properly, please <b>flag your Commander in the deckbuilder</b> or put it in a separate section called "Commander"!</div>
<div id="edh_specify_commander">

function nk_cardlink_init() {
	nk_deckstats_lng = LNG;
	
	//https://hacks.mozilla.org/2009/07/cross-site-xmlhttprequest-with-cors/
	try {
		if (COUNTRY != 'PL' && 'withCredentials' in new XMLHttpRequest()) {

<div class="any_dialog" id="download_regsheet_dialog" title="Download Deck Sheet">
<p>
To play your deck at an official ("DCI-sanctioned") tournament you need a deck registration sheet. Here you can download such a sheet pre-filled with the cards in this deck!	</p>
<div style="margin-top: .5em">
<label for="download_regsheet_sort">Sort cards by:</label>
<select id="download_regsheet_sort" class="ui-corner-all">
<option value="name">Card Name</option>
<option value="amount">Amount</option>
<option value="type">Type</option>
<option value="none">do not sort</option>
</select>
</div>
<div style="margin-top: .5em">
<label>
<input type="checkbox" checked="checked" id="download_regsheet_dci_details">
Include my DCI number and name </label>
(-&gt;
<a href="https://deckstats.net/settings/?lng=en" target="_blank">
Your Settings</a>)
</div>
<p>
<i>
Please note: This is not an official DCI service. So please always make extra sure that the sheet contains all the cards in your deck and fulfils all DCI requirements. If you notice anything wrong, please let us know! DCI is a trademark of of Wizards of the Coast LLC.
</i>
</p>
</div>

<div id="deck_tabs-tools">
<div class="section_header" id="deck_code_header">Embed Into Forums or Website</div>
<div class="inhalt2">
<div style="margin-bottom: 5px;">
For forums and blogs please select one of the BB-Code options. For websites and forums that support HTML (e.g. Wizards Community Forums) you can use the HTML options!	</div>
<div style="margin-top: 1em;">
<div>
<select name="code_type" id="code_type">
<option value="bb_deck">BB-Code with DECK tags (for MTG-Forum.de)</option>
<option value="bb_url">BB-Code with URL tags (recommended for most forums)</option>
<option value="markdown">Markdown List (for reddit)</option>
<option value="markdown_table">Markdown Table (for reddit)</option>
<option value="html_wide">HTML code for high table</option>
<option value="html_normal">HTML for wide table (recommended for Wizards Community)</option>
</select>
<select name="code_extended" id="code_extended">
<option value="0">Normal View</option>
<option value="1">Extended View (with mana symbols)</option>
</select>
<input class="button" type="submit" name="get_code" id="get_code" value="Generate Embed Code" />
</div>
<div>
<label id="code_html_nl_label">
<input name="code_html_nl" id="code_html_nl" type="checkbox" style="border: 0" />
Use linebreaks in HTML code (disable for Wizards Community) </label>
</div>
<script type="text/javascript">
			function generate_code_action(e) {
				e.preventDefault();

				document.location.href = 'https://deckstats.net/decks/122209/1170811-oloro-edh-/en?get_code=1' +
					'&code_type=' + $('#code_type').val() +
					'&code_extended=' + $('#code_extended').val() +
					'&code_html_nl=' + ($('#code_html_nl').is(':checked')? 'on' : 'off');
			}

			$(function(){
				$('#get_code').click(generate_code_action);

				$('#code_type,#code_extended,#code_html_nl').change(function(e) {
					$('#code_result').hide();
				});
				$('#code_type').change(function(e) {
					if($(this).val().substr(0, 4) == 'html') {
						$('#code_html_nl_label').show();
					} else {
						$('#code_html_nl_label').hide();
					}
				});
				updateCodeType($('#code_type')[0]);
			});
		</script>
</div>
</div>

<div class="any_dialog" id="download_regsheet_dialog" title="Download Deck Sheet">
<p>
To play your deck at an official ("DCI-sanctioned") tournament you need a deck registration sheet. Here you can download such a sheet pre-filled with the cards in this deck!	</p>
<div style="margin-top: .5em">
<label for="download_regsheet_sort">Sort cards by:</label>
<select id="download_regsheet_sort" class="ui-corner-all">
<option value="name">Card Name</option>
<option value="amount">Amount</option>
<option value="type">Type</option>
<option value="none">do not sort</option>
</select>
</div>
<div style="margin-top: .5em">
<label>
<input type="checkbox" checked="checked" id="download_regsheet_dci_details">
Include my DCI number and name </label>
(-&gt;
<a href="https://deckstats.net/settings/?lng=en" target="_blank">
Your Settings</a>)
</div>
<p>
<i>
Please note: This is not an official DCI service. So please always make extra sure that the sheet contains all the cards in your deck and fulfils all DCI requirements. If you notice anything wrong, please let us know! DCI is a trademark of of Wizards of the Coast LLC.
</i>
</p>
</div>

<div class="section_header" id="deck_code_header">Embed Into Forums or Website</div>
<div class="inhalt2">
<div style="margin-bottom: 5px;">
For forums and blogs please select one of the BB-Code options. For websites and forums that support HTML (e.g. Wizards Community Forums) you can use the HTML options!	</div>
<div style="margin-top: 1em;">
<div>
<select name="code_type" id="code_type">
<option value="bb_deck">BB-Code with DECK tags (for MTG-Forum.de)</option>
<option value="bb_url">BB-Code with URL tags (recommended for most forums)</option>
<option value="markdown">Markdown List (for reddit)</option>
<option value="markdown_table">Markdown Table (for reddit)</option>
<option value="html_wide">HTML code for high table</option>
<option value="html_normal">HTML for wide table (recommended for Wizards Community)</option>
</select>
<select name="code_extended" id="code_extended">
<option value="0">Normal View</option>
<option value="1">Extended View (with mana symbols)</option>
</select>
<input class="button" type="submit" name="get_code" id="get_code" value="Generate Embed Code" />
</div>
<div>
<label id="code_html_nl_label">
<input name="code_html_nl" id="code_html_nl" type="checkbox" style="border: 0" />
Use linebreaks in HTML code (disable for Wizards Community) </label>
</div>
<script type="text/javascript">
			function generate_code_action(e) {
				e.preventDefault();

				document.location.href = 'https://deckstats.net/decks/99694/1238538-mono-brown-traxos-2/en?get_code=1' +
					'&code_type=' + $('#code_type').val() +
					'&code_extended=' + $('#code_extended').val() +
					'&code_html_nl=' + ($('#code_html_nl').is(':checked')? 'on' : 'off');
			}

			$(function(){
				$('#get_code').click(generate_code_action);

				$('#code_type,#code_extended,#code_html_nl').change(function(e) {
					$('#code_result').hide();
				});
				$('#code_type').change(function(e) {
					if($(this).val().substr(0, 4) == 'html') {
						$('#code_html_nl_label').show();
					} else {
						$('#code_html_nl_label').hide();
					}
				});
				updateCodeType($('#code_type')[0]);
			});
		</script>
</div>
</div>

<div class="any_dialog" id="download_regsheet_dialog" title="Download Deck Sheet">
<p>
To play your deck at an official ("DCI-sanctioned") tournament you need a deck registration sheet. Here you can download such a sheet pre-filled with the cards in this deck!	</p>
<div style="margin-top: .5em">
<label for="download_regsheet_sort">Sort cards by:</label>
<select id="download_regsheet_sort" class="ui-corner-all">
<option value="name">Card Name</option>
<option value="amount">Amount</option>
<option value="type">Type</option>
<option value="none">do not sort</option>
</select>
</div>
<div style="margin-top: .5em">
<label>
<input type="checkbox" checked="checked" id="download_regsheet_dci_details">
Include my DCI number and name </label>
(-&gt;
<a href="https://deckstats.net/settings/?lng=en" target="_blank">
Your Settings</a>)
</div>
<p>
<i>
Please note: This is not an official DCI service. So please always make extra sure that the sheet contains all the cards in your deck and fulfils all DCI requirements. If you notice anything wrong, please let us know! DCI is a trademark of of Wizards of the Coast LLC.
</i>
</p>

<div id="deck_tabs-tools">
<div class="section_header" id="deck_code_header">Embed Into Forums or Website</div>
<div class="inhalt2">
<div style="margin-bottom: 5px;">
For forums and blogs please select one of the BB-Code options. For websites and forums that support HTML (e.g. Wizards Community Forums) you can use the HTML options!	</div>
<div style="margin-top: 1em;">
<div>
<select name="code_type" id="code_type">
<option value="bb_deck">BB-Code with DECK tags (for MTG-Forum.de)</option>
<option value="bb_url">BB-Code with URL tags (recommended for most forums)</option>
<option value="markdown">Markdown List (for reddit)</option>
<option value="markdown_table">Markdown Table (for reddit)</option>
<option value="html_wide">HTML code for high table</option>
<option value="html_normal">HTML for wide table (recommended for Wizards Community)</option>
</select>
<select name="code_extended" id="code_extended">
<option value="0">Normal View</option>
<option value="1">Extended View (with mana symbols)</option>
</select>
<input class="button" type="submit" name="get_code" id="get_code" value="Generate Embed Code" />
</div>
<div>
<label id="code_html_nl_label">
<input name="code_html_nl" id="code_html_nl" type="checkbox" style="border: 0" />
Use linebreaks in HTML code (disable for Wizards Community) </label>
</div>
<script type="text/javascript">
			function generate_code_action(e) {
				e.preventDefault();

				document.location.href = 'https://deckstats.net/decks/39477/1237470-artificial-infect-glissa-the-t/en?get_code=1' +
					'&code_type=' + $('#code_type').val() +
					'&code_extended=' + $('#code_extended').val() +
					'&code_html_nl=' + ($('#code_html_nl').is(':checked')? 'on' : 'off');
			}

			$(function(){
				$('#get_code').click(generate_code_action);

				$('#code_type,#code_extended,#code_html_nl').change(function(e) {
					$('#code_result').hide();
				});
				$('#code_type').change(function(e) {
					if($(this).val().substr(0, 4) == 'html') {
						$('#code_html_nl_label').show();
					} else {
						$('#code_html_nl_label').hide();
					}
				});
				updateCodeType($('#code_type')[0]);
			});
		</script>
</div>
</div>

function nk_cardlink_init() {
	nk_deckstats_lng = LNG;
	
	//https://hacks.mozilla.org/2009/07/cross-site-xmlhttprequest-with-cors/
	try {
		if (COUNTRY != 'PL' && 'withCredentials' in new XMLHttpRequest()) {
			nk_cardlink_external = 'https://www.mtg-forum.de/db/get.php';

		}
	} catch(ex) {
		//this catches IE8, which may not allow 'new XMLHttpRequest()'
		nk_cardlink_external = PATH+'/db_tunnel.php';
	}
		
	
	nk_cardlink_lng = (nk_deckstats_lng == 'de'? 'de' : 'en');

	nk_cardlink_all = true;

<div id="deck_tabs-tools">
<div class="section_header" id="deck_code_header">Embed Into Forums or Website</div>
<div class="inhalt2">
<div style="margin-bottom: 5px;">
For forums and blogs please select one of the BB-Code options. For websites and forums that support HTML (e.g. Wizards Community Forums) you can use the HTML options!	</div>
<div style="margin-top: 1em;">
<div>
<select name="code_type" id="code_type">
<option value="bb_deck">BB-Code with DECK tags (for MTG-Forum.de)</option>
<option value="bb_url">BB-Code with URL tags (recommended for most forums)</option>
<option value="markdown">Markdown List (for reddit)</option>
<option value="markdown_table">Markdown Table (for reddit)</option>
<option value="html_wide">HTML code for high table</option>
<option value="html_normal">HTML for wide table (recommended for Wizards Community)</option>
</select>
<select name="code_extended" id="code_extended">
<option value="0">Normal View</option>
<option value="1">Extended View (with mana symbols)</option>
</select>
<input class="button" type="submit" name="get_code" id="get_code" value="Generate Embed Code" />
</div>
<div>
<label id="code_html_nl_label">
<input name="code_html_nl" id="code_html_nl" type="checkbox" style="border: 0" />
Use linebreaks in HTML code (disable for Wizards Community) </label>
</div>
<script type="text/javascript">
			function generate_code_action(e) {
				e.preventDefault();

				document.location.href = 'https://deckstats.net/decks/87262/1238532-hapatra-realista/en?get_code=1' +
					'&code_type=' + $('#code_type').val() +
					'&code_extended=' + $('#code_extended').val() +
					'&code_html_nl=' + ($('#code_html_nl').is(':checked')? 'on' : 'off');
			}

			$(function(){
				$('#get_code').click(generate_code_action);

				$('#code_type,#code_extended,#code_html_nl').change(function(e) {
					$('#code_result').hide();
				});
				$('#code_type').change(function(e) {
					if($(this).val().substr(0, 4) == 'html') {
						$('#code_html_nl_label').show();
					} else {
						$('#code_html_nl_label').hide();
					}
				});
				updateCodeType($('#code_type')[0]);
			});
		</script>
</div>
</div>

With this tool you can get recommendations for new cards to add to your EDH deck, based on which cards other players play with this Commander.	To make sure your deck is analyzed properly, please <b>flag your Commander in the deckbuilder</b> or put it in a separate section called "Commander"!</div>

function nk_cardlink_init() {
	nk_deckstats_lng = LNG;
	
	//https://hacks.mozilla.org/2009/07/cross-site-xmlhttprequest-with-cors/
	try {
		if (COUNTRY != 'PL' && 'withCredentials' in new XMLHttpRequest()) {
			nk_cardlink_external = 'https://www.mtg-forum.de/db/get.php';

		//this catches IE8, which may not allow 'new XMLHttpRequest()'

	}

<div id="deck_tabs-tools">
<div class="section_header" id="deck_code_header">Embed Into Forums or Website</div>
<div class="inhalt2">
<div style="margin-bottom: 5px;">
For forums and blogs please select one of the BB-Code options. For websites and forums that support HTML (e.g. Wizards Community Forums) you can use the HTML options!	</div>
<div style="margin-top: 1em;">
<div>
<select name="code_type" id="code_type">
<option value="bb_deck">BB-Code with DECK tags (for MTG-Forum.de)</option>
<option value="bb_url">BB-Code with URL tags (recommended for most forums)</option>
<option value="markdown">Markdown List (for reddit)</option>
<option value="markdown_table">Markdown Table (for reddit)</option>
<option value="html_wide">HTML code for high table</option>
<option value="html_normal">HTML for wide table (recommended for Wizards Community)</option>
</select>
<select name="code_extended" id="code_extended">
<option value="0">Normal View</option>
<option value="1">Extended View (with mana symbols)</option>
</select>
<input class="button" type="submit" name="get_code" id="get_code" value="Generate Embed Code" />
</div>
<div>
<label id="code_html_nl_label">
<input name="code_html_nl" id="code_html_nl" type="checkbox" style="border: 0" />
Use linebreaks in HTML code (disable for Wizards Community) </label>
</div>
<script type="text/javascript">
			function generate_code_action(e) {
				e.preventDefault();

				document.location.href = 'https://deckstats.net/decks/71266/1232474-equipment-angel-mono-w/en?get_code=1' +
					'&code_type=' + $('#code_type').val() +
					'&code_extended=' + $('#code_extended').val() +
					'&code_html_nl=' + ($('#code_html_nl').is(':checked')? 'on' : 'off');
			}

			$(function(){
				$('#get_code').click(generate_code_action);

				$('#code_type,#code_extended,#code_html_nl').change(function(e) {
					$('#code_result').hide();
				});
				$('#code_type').change(function(e) {
					if($(this).val().substr(0, 4) == 'html') {
						$('#code_html_nl_label').show();
					} else {
						$('#code_html_nl_label').hide();
					}
				});
				updateCodeType($('#code_type')[0]);
			});
		</script>
</div>
</div>

With this tool you can get recommendations for new cards to add to your EDH deck, based on which cards other players play with this Commander.	To make sure your deck is analyzed properly, please <b>flag your Commander in the deckbuilder</b> or put it in a separate section called "Commander"!</div>

function nk_cardlink_init() {
	nk_deckstats_lng = LNG;
	
	//https://hacks.mozilla.org/2009/07/cross-site-xmlhttprequest-with-cors/
	try {
		if (COUNTRY != 'PL' && 'withCredentials' in new XMLHttpRequest()) {
			nk_cardlink_external = 'https://www.mtg-forum.de/db/get.php';
		} else {
			nk_cardlink_external = PATH+'/db_tunnel.php';
		}
	} catch(ex) {
		//this catches IE8, which may not allow 'new XMLHttpRequest()'
		nk_cardlink_external = PATH+'/db_tunnel.php';
	}
		
	
	nk_cardlink_lng = (nk_deckstats_lng == 'de'? 'de' : 'en');

<div id="deck_tabs-tools">
<div class="section_header" id="deck_code_header">Embed Into Forums or Website</div>
<div class="inhalt2">
<div style="margin-bottom: 5px;">
For forums and blogs please select one of the BB-Code options. For websites and forums that support HTML (e.g. Wizards Community Forums) you can use the HTML options!	</div>
<div style="margin-top: 1em;">
<div>
<select name="code_type" id="code_type">
<option value="bb_deck">BB-Code with DECK tags (for MTG-Forum.de)</option>
<option value="bb_url">BB-Code with URL tags (recommended for most forums)</option>
<option value="markdown">Markdown List (for reddit)</option>
<option value="markdown_table">Markdown Table (for reddit)</option>
<option value="html_wide">HTML code for high table</option>
<option value="html_normal">HTML for wide table (recommended for Wizards Community)</option>
</select>
<select name="code_extended" id="code_extended">
<option value="0">Normal View</option>
<option value="1">Extended View (with mana symbols)</option>
</select>
<input class="button" type="submit" name="get_code" id="get_code" value="Generate Embed Code" />
</div>
<div>
<label id="code_html_nl_label">
<input name="code_html_nl" id="code_html_nl" type="checkbox" style="border: 0" />
Use linebreaks in HTML code (disable for Wizards Community) </label>
</div>
<script type="text/javascript">
			function generate_code_action(e) {
				e.preventDefault();

				document.location.href = 'https://deckstats.net/decks/122209/1220477-marchesa-edh-/en?get_code=1' +
					'&code_type=' + $('#code_type').val() +
					'&code_extended=' + $('#code_extended').val() +
					'&code_html_nl=' + ($('#code_html_nl').is(':checked')? 'on' : 'off');
			}

			$(function(){
				$('#get_code').click(generate_code_action);

				$('#code_type,#code_extended,#code_html_nl').change(function(e) {
					$('#code_result').hide();
				});
				$('#code_type').change(function(e) {
					if($(this).val().substr(0, 4) == 'html') {
						$('#code_html_nl_label').show();
					} else {
						$('#code_html_nl_label').hide();
					}
				});
				updateCodeType($('#code_type')[0]);
			});
		</script>
</div>
</div>

<div id="deck_tabs-edh">
<div class="inhalt2">
With this tool you can get recommendations for new cards to add to your EDH deck, based on which cards other players play with this Commander.	To make sure your deck is analyzed properly, please <b>flag your Commander in the deckbuilder</b> or put it in a separate section called "Commander"!</div>
<div id="edh_specify_commander">
<h3 class="section_header">Specify Commander</h3>
<div class="inhalt2">
<div>
Unfortunately, we could not automatically detect the commander in this deck. Please choose it here: </div>

</div>

<script>
var PATH = "\/\/deckstats.net";
var LNG = "en";
var COUNTRY = "DK";
var user_logged_in = false;

//as a function so it can be called when async loading of cardlink is done
function nk_cardlink_init() {
	nk_deckstats_lng = LNG;
	
	//https://hacks.mozilla.org/2009/07/cross-site-xmlhttprequest-with-cors/
	try {
		if (COUNTRY != 'PL' && 'withCredentials' in new XMLHttpRequest()) {
			nk_cardlink_external = 'https://www.mtg-forum.de/db/get.php';
		} else {
			nk_cardlink_external = PATH+'/db_tunnel.php';
		}
	} catch(ex) {
		//this catches IE8, which may not allow 'new XMLHttpRequest()'
		nk_cardlink_external = PATH+'/db_tunnel.php';
	}
		
	
	nk_cardlink_lng = (nk_deckstats_lng == 'de'? 'de' : 'en');
	nk_use_mana_sprites = true;
	nk_cardlink_all = true;
};

nk_cardlink_init();

	//SMF data
	smf_user_id = 0;	
	smf_user_name = "Guest";
	//for session validation in comments
	smf_session_var = "be762b0cd8f6";
	smf_session_id = "63daff6245c3e44e4bfd96052f552af6";

<div id="deck_tabs-tools">
<div class="section_header" id="deck_code_header">Embed Into Forums or Website</div>
<div class="inhalt2">
<div style="margin-bottom: 5px;">
For forums and blogs please select one of the BB-Code options. For websites and forums that support HTML (e.g. Wizards Community Forums) you can use the HTML options!	</div>
<div style="margin-top: 1em;">
<div>
<select name="code_type" id="code_type">
<option value="bb_deck">BB-Code with DECK tags (for MTG-Forum.de)</option>
<option value="bb_url">BB-Code with URL tags (recommended for most forums)</option>
<option value="markdown">Markdown List (for reddit)</option>
<option value="markdown_table">Markdown Table (for reddit)</option>
<option value="html_wide">HTML code for high table</option>
<option value="html_normal">HTML for wide table (recommended for Wizards Community)</option>
</select>
<select name="code_extended" id="code_extended">
<option value="0">Normal View</option>
<option value="1">Extended View (with mana symbols)</option>
</select>
<input class="button" type="submit" name="get_code" id="get_code" value="Generate Embed Code" />
</div>
<div>
<label id="code_html_nl_label">
<input name="code_html_nl" id="code_html_nl" type="checkbox" style="border: 0" />
Use linebreaks in HTML code (disable for Wizards Community) </label>
</div>
<script type="text/javascript">
			function generate_code_action(e) {
				e.preventDefault();

				document.location.href = 'https://deckstats.net/decks/127880/1238328-haunt/en?get_code=1' +
					'&code_type=' + $('#code_type').val() +
					'&code_extended=' + $('#code_extended').val() +
					'&code_html_nl=' + ($('#code_html_nl').is(':checked')? 'on' : 'off');
			}

			$(function(){
				$('#get_code').click(generate_code_action);

				$('#code_type,#code_extended,#code_html_nl').change(function(e) {
					$('#code_result').hide();
				});
				$('#code_type').change(function(e) {
					if($(this).val().substr(0, 4) == 'html') {
						$('#code_html_nl_label').show();
					} else {
						$('#code_html_nl_label').hide();
					}
				});
				updateCodeType($('#code_type')[0]);
			});
		</script>
</div>
</div>

<div class="section_header" id="deck_code_header">Embed Into Forums or Website</div>
<div class="inhalt2">
<div style="margin-bottom: 5px;">
For forums and blogs please select one of the BB-Code options. For websites and forums that support HTML (e.g. Wizards Community Forums) you can use the HTML options!	</div>
<div style="margin-top: 1em;">
<div>
<select name="code_type" id="code_type">
<option value="bb_deck">BB-Code with DECK tags (for MTG-Forum.de)</option>
<option value="bb_url">BB-Code with URL tags (recommended for most forums)</option>
<option value="markdown">Markdown List (for reddit)</option>
<option value="markdown_table">Markdown Table (for reddit)</option>
<option value="html_wide">HTML code for high table</option>
<option value="html_normal">HTML for wide table (recommended for Wizards Community)</option>
</select>
<select name="code_extended" id="code_extended">
<option value="0">Normal View</option>
<option value="1">Extended View (with mana symbols)</option>
</select>
<input class="button" type="submit" name="get_code" id="get_code" value="Generate Embed Code" />
</div>
<div>
<label id="code_html_nl_label">
<input name="code_html_nl" id="code_html_nl" type="checkbox" style="border: 0" />
Use linebreaks in HTML code (disable for Wizards Community) </label>
</div>
<script type="text/javascript">
			function generate_code_action(e) {
				e.preventDefault();

				document.location.href = 'https://deckstats.net/decks/71266/1218196-all-the-walls-/en?get_code=1' +
					'&code_type=' + $('#code_type').val() +
					'&code_extended=' + $('#code_extended').val() +
					'&code_html_nl=' + ($('#code_html_nl').is(':checked')? 'on' : 'off');
			}

			$(function(){
				$('#get_code').click(generate_code_action);

				$('#code_type,#code_extended,#code_html_nl').change(function(e) {
					$('#code_result').hide();
				});
				$('#code_type').change(function(e) {
					if($(this).val().substr(0, 4) == 'html') {
						$('#code_html_nl_label').show();
					} else {
						$('#code_html_nl_label').hide();
					}
				});
				updateCodeType($('#code_type')[0]);
			});
		</script>
</div>
</div>

	nk_deckstats_lng = LNG;

	try {
		if (COUNTRY != 'PL' && 'withCredentials' in new XMLHttpRequest()) {

<div id="deck_tabs-tools">
<div class="section_header" id="deck_code_header">Embed Into Forums or Website</div>
<div class="inhalt2">
<div style="margin-bottom: 5px;">
For forums and blogs please select one of the BB-Code options. For websites and forums that support HTML (e.g. Wizards Community Forums) you can use the HTML options!	</div>
<div style="margin-top: 1em;">
<div>
<select name="code_type" id="code_type">
<option value="bb_deck">BB-Code with DECK tags (for MTG-Forum.de)</option>
<option value="bb_url">BB-Code with URL tags (recommended for most forums)</option>
<option value="markdown">Markdown List (for reddit)</option>
<option value="markdown_table">Markdown Table (for reddit)</option>
<option value="html_wide">HTML code for high table</option>
<option value="html_normal">HTML for wide table (recommended for Wizards Community)</option>
</select>
<select name="code_extended" id="code_extended">
<option value="0">Normal View</option>
<option value="1">Extended View (with mana symbols)</option>
</select>
<input class="button" type="submit" name="get_code" id="get_code" value="Generate Embed Code" />
</div>
<div>
<label id="code_html_nl_label">
<input name="code_html_nl" id="code_html_nl" type="checkbox" style="border: 0" />
Use linebreaks in HTML code (disable for Wizards Community) </label>
</div>
<script type="text/javascript">
			function generate_code_action(e) {
				e.preventDefault();

				document.location.href = 'https://deckstats.net/decks/128021/1238527-ezuri-s-gefolgeleute/en?get_code=1' +
					'&code_type=' + $('#code_type').val() +
					'&code_extended=' + $('#code_extended').val() +
					'&code_html_nl=' + ($('#code_html_nl').is(':checked')? 'on' : 'off');
			}

			$(function(){
				$('#get_code').click(generate_code_action);

				$('#code_type,#code_extended,#code_html_nl').change(function(e) {
					$('#code_result').hide();
				});
				$('#code_type').change(function(e) {
					if($(this).val().substr(0, 4) == 'html') {
						$('#code_html_nl_label').show();
					} else {
						$('#code_html_nl_label').hide();
					}
				});
				updateCodeType($('#code_type')[0]);
			});
		</script>
</div>
</div>

</button>

<label>
<input id="download_deck_include_comments" checked="checked" type="checkbox">
Include card comments (.dec)
</label>
</p>
</div>
<div class="any_dialog" id="download_regsheet_dialog" title="Download Deck Sheet">
<p>
To play your deck at an official ("DCI-sanctioned") tournament you need a deck registration sheet. Here you can download such a sheet pre-filled with the cards in this deck!	</p>
<div style="margin-top: .5em">
<label for="download_regsheet_sort">Sort cards by:</label>
<select id="download_regsheet_sort" class="ui-corner-all">
<option value="name">Card Name</option>
<option value="amount">Amount</option>
<option value="type">Type</option>
<option value="none">do not sort</option>
</select>
</div>
<div style="margin-top: .5em">
<label>
<input type="checkbox" checked="checked" id="download_regsheet_dci_details">
Include my DCI number and name </label>
(-&gt;
<a href="https://deckstats.net/settings/?lng=en" target="_blank">
Your Settings</a>)
</div>
<p>
<i>
Please note: This is not an official DCI service. So please always make extra sure that the sheet contains all the cards in your deck and fulfils all DCI requirements. If you notice anything wrong, please let us know! DCI is a trademark of of Wizards of the Coast LLC.
</i>
</p>
</div>

<div id="deck_tabs-tools">
<div class="section_header" id="deck_code_header">Embed Into Forums or Website</div>
<div class="inhalt2">
<div style="margin-bottom: 5px;">
For forums and blogs please select one of the BB-Code options. For websites and forums that support HTML (e.g. Wizards Community Forums) you can use the HTML options!	</div>
<div style="margin-top: 1em;">
<div>
<select name="code_type" id="code_type">
<option value="bb_deck">BB-Code with DECK tags (for MTG-Forum.de)</option>
<option value="bb_url">BB-Code with URL tags (recommended for most forums)</option>
<option value="markdown">Markdown List (for reddit)</option>
<option value="markdown_table">Markdown Table (for reddit)</option>
<option value="html_wide">HTML code for high table</option>
<option value="html_normal">HTML for wide table (recommended for Wizards Community)</option>
</select>
<select name="code_extended" id="code_extended">
<option value="0">Normal View</option>
<option value="1">Extended View (with mana symbols)</option>
</select>
<input class="button" type="submit" name="get_code" id="get_code" value="Generate Embed Code" />
</div>
<div>
<label id="code_html_nl_label">
<input name="code_html_nl" id="code_html_nl" type="checkbox" style="border: 0" />
Use linebreaks in HTML code (disable for Wizards Community) </label>
</div>
<script type="text/javascript">
			function generate_code_action(e) {
				e.preventDefault();

				document.location.href = 'https://deckstats.net/decks/35429/1219671-muldrotha-recursion/en?get_code=1' +
					'&code_type=' + $('#code_type').val() +
					'&code_extended=' + $('#code_extended').val() +
					'&code_html_nl=' + ($('#code_html_nl').is(':checked')? 'on' : 'off');
			}

			$(function(){
				$('#get_code').click(generate_code_action);

				$('#code_type,#code_extended,#code_html_nl').change(function(e) {
					$('#code_result').hide();
				});
				$('#code_type').change(function(e) {
					if($(this).val().substr(0, 4) == 'html') {
						$('#code_html_nl_label').show();
					} else {
						$('#code_html_nl_label').hide();
					}
				});
				updateCodeType($('#code_type')[0]);
			});
		</script>
</div>
</div>

<div class="inhalt2">
With this tool you can get recommendations for new cards to add to your EDH deck, based on which cards other players play with this Commander.	To make sure your deck is analyzed properly, please <b>flag your Commander in the deckbuilder</b> or put it in a separate section called "Commander"!</div>

	nk_deckstats_lng = LNG;

	try {
		if (COUNTRY != 'PL' && 'withCredentials' in new XMLHttpRequest()) {

<div class="any_dialog" id="download_regsheet_dialog" title="Download Deck Sheet">
<p>
To play your deck at an official ("DCI-sanctioned") tournament you need a deck registration sheet. Here you can download such a sheet pre-filled with the cards in this deck!	</p>
<div style="margin-top: .5em">
<label for="download_regsheet_sort">Sort cards by:</label>
<select id="download_regsheet_sort" class="ui-corner-all">
<option value="name">Card Name</option>
<option value="amount">Amount</option>
<option value="type">Type</option>
<option value="none">do not sort</option>
</select>
</div>
<div style="margin-top: .5em">
<label>
<input type="checkbox" checked="checked" id="download_regsheet_dci_details">
Include my DCI number and name </label>
(-&gt;
<a href="https://deckstats.net/settings/?lng=en" target="_blank">
Your Settings</a>)
</div>
<p>
<i>
Please note: This is not an official DCI service. So please always make extra sure that the sheet contains all the cards in your deck and fulfils all DCI requirements. If you notice anything wrong, please let us know! DCI is a trademark of of Wizards of the Coast LLC.
</i>
</p>

<div id="deck_tabs-tools">
<div class="section_header" id="deck_code_header">Embed Into Forums or Website</div>
<div class="inhalt2">
<div style="margin-bottom: 5px;">
For forums and blogs please select one of the BB-Code options. For websites and forums that support HTML (e.g. Wizards Community Forums) you can use the HTML options!	</div>
<div style="margin-top: 1em;">
<div>
<select name="code_type" id="code_type">
<option value="bb_deck">BB-Code with DECK tags (for MTG-Forum.de)</option>
<option value="bb_url">BB-Code with URL tags (recommended for most forums)</option>
<option value="markdown">Markdown List (for reddit)</option>
<option value="markdown_table">Markdown Table (for reddit)</option>
<option value="html_wide">HTML code for high table</option>
<option value="html_normal">HTML for wide table (recommended for Wizards Community)</option>
</select>
<select name="code_extended" id="code_extended">
<option value="0">Normal View</option>
<option value="1">Extended View (with mana symbols)</option>
</select>
<input class="button" type="submit" name="get_code" id="get_code" value="Generate Embed Code" />
</div>
<div>
<label id="code_html_nl_label">
<input name="code_html_nl" id="code_html_nl" type="checkbox" style="border: 0" />
Use linebreaks in HTML code (disable for Wizards Community) </label>
</div>
<script type="text/javascript">
			function generate_code_action(e) {
				e.preventDefault();

				document.location.href = 'https://deckstats.net/decks/35429/1105407-animar-semi-competitive-/en?get_code=1' +
					'&code_type=' + $('#code_type').val() +
					'&code_extended=' + $('#code_extended').val() +
					'&code_html_nl=' + ($('#code_html_nl').is(':checked')? 'on' : 'off');
			}

			$(function(){
				$('#get_code').click(generate_code_action);

				$('#code_type,#code_extended,#code_html_nl').change(function(e) {
					$('#code_result').hide();
				});
				$('#code_type').change(function(e) {
					if($(this).val().substr(0, 4) == 'html') {
						$('#code_html_nl_label').show();
					} else {
						$('#code_html_nl_label').hide();
					}
				});
				updateCodeType($('#code_type')[0]);
			});
		</script>
</div>
</div>

function nk_cardlink_init() {
	nk_deckstats_lng = LNG;
	
	//https://hacks.mozilla.org/2009/07/cross-site-xmlhttprequest-with-cors/
	try {
		if (COUNTRY != 'PL' && 'withCredentials' in new XMLHttpRequest()) {
			nk_cardlink_external = 'https://www.mtg-forum.de/db/get.php';

			nk_cardlink_external = PATH+'/db_tunnel.php';

	} catch(ex) {
		//this catches IE8, which may not allow 'new XMLHttpRequest()'
		nk_cardlink_external = PATH+'/db_tunnel.php';
	}

<div class="any_dialog" id="download_regsheet_dialog" title="Download Deck Sheet">
<p>
To play your deck at an official ("DCI-sanctioned") tournament you need a deck registration sheet. Here you can download such a sheet pre-filled with the cards in this deck!	</p>
<div style="margin-top: .5em">
<label for="download_regsheet_sort">Sort cards by:</label>
<select id="download_regsheet_sort" class="ui-corner-all">
<option value="name">Card Name</option>
<option value="amount">Amount</option>
<option value="type">Type</option>
<option value="none">do not sort</option>
</select>
</div>
<div style="margin-top: .5em">
<label>
<input type="checkbox" checked="checked" id="download_regsheet_dci_details">
Include my DCI number and name </label>
(-&gt;
<a href="https://deckstats.net/settings/?lng=en" target="_blank">
Your Settings</a>)
</div>
<p>
<i>
Please note: This is not an official DCI service. So please always make extra sure that the sheet contains all the cards in your deck and fulfils all DCI requirements. If you notice anything wrong, please let us know! DCI is a trademark of of Wizards of the Coast LLC.
</i>
</p>
</div>

<h3>
Maybeboard <span class="amount">(9)</span>
</h3>
<div class="deck_overview_card" data-group-section="Maybeboard" data-section-index="0" data-group-section="" data-group-type="Other" data-group-type-extended="Other" data-group-color="Colorless" data-group-cc="" data-group-rarity="Other">

<div id="deck_tabs-tools">
<div class="section_header" id="deck_code_header">Embed Into Forums or Website</div>
<div class="inhalt2">
<div style="margin-bottom: 5px;">
For forums and blogs please select one of the BB-Code options. For websites and forums that support HTML (e.g. Wizards Community Forums) you can use the HTML options!	</div>
<div style="margin-top: 1em;">
<div>
<select name="code_type" id="code_type">
<option value="bb_deck">BB-Code with DECK tags (for MTG-Forum.de)</option>
<option value="bb_url">BB-Code with URL tags (recommended for most forums)</option>
<option value="markdown">Markdown List (for reddit)</option>
<option value="markdown_table">Markdown Table (for reddit)</option>
<option value="html_wide">HTML code for high table</option>
<option value="html_normal">HTML for wide table (recommended for Wizards Community)</option>
</select>
<select name="code_extended" id="code_extended">
<option value="0">Normal View</option>
<option value="1">Extended View (with mana symbols)</option>
</select>
<input class="button" type="submit" name="get_code" id="get_code" value="Generate Embed Code" />
</div>
<div>
<label id="code_html_nl_label">
<input name="code_html_nl" id="code_html_nl" type="checkbox" style="border: 0" />
Use linebreaks in HTML code (disable for Wizards Community) </label>
</div>
<script type="text/javascript">
			function generate_code_action(e) {
				e.preventDefault();

				document.location.href = 'https://deckstats.net/decks/84929/1206098-ravos-tymna/en?get_code=1' +
					'&code_type=' + $('#code_type').val() +
					'&code_extended=' + $('#code_extended').val() +
					'&code_html_nl=' + ($('#code_html_nl').is(':checked')? 'on' : 'off');
			}

			$(function(){
				$('#get_code').click(generate_code_action);

				$('#code_type,#code_extended,#code_html_nl').change(function(e) {
					$('#code_result').hide();
				});
				$('#code_type').change(function(e) {
					if($(this).val().substr(0, 4) == 'html') {
						$('#code_html_nl_label').show();
					} else {
						$('#code_html_nl_label').hide();
					}
				});
				updateCodeType($('#code_type')[0]);
			});
		</script>
</div>
</div>

<div id="deck_tabs-edh">
<div class="inhalt2">
With this tool you can get recommendations for new cards to add to your EDH deck, based on which cards other players play with this Commander.	To make sure your deck is analyzed properly, please <b>flag your Commander in the deckbuilder</b> or put it in a separate section called "Commander"!</div>
<div id="edh_specify_commander">

var PATH = "\/\/deckstats.net";
var LNG = "en";
var COUNTRY = "DK";
var user_logged_in = false;

//as a function so it can be called when async loading of cardlink is done
function nk_cardlink_init() {
	nk_deckstats_lng = LNG;
	
	//https://hacks.mozilla.org/2009/07/cross-site-xmlhttprequest-with-cors/
	try {
		if (COUNTRY != 'PL' && 'withCredentials' in new XMLHttpRequest()) {
			nk_cardlink_external = 'https://www.mtg-forum.de/db/get.php';
		} else {
			nk_cardlink_external = PATH+'/db_tunnel.php';
		}
	} catch(ex) {
		//this catches IE8, which may not allow 'new XMLHttpRequest()'
		nk_cardlink_external = PATH+'/db_tunnel.php';
	}
		
	
	nk_cardlink_lng = (nk_deckstats_lng == 'de'? 'de' : 'en');
	nk_use_mana_sprites = true;
	nk_cardlink_all = true;
};

<div id="deck_tabs-tools">
<div class="section_header" id="deck_code_header">Embed Into Forums or Website</div>
<div class="inhalt2">
<div style="margin-bottom: 5px;">
For forums and blogs please select one of the BB-Code options. For websites and forums that support HTML (e.g. Wizards Community Forums) you can use the HTML options!	</div>
<div style="margin-top: 1em;">
<div>
<select name="code_type" id="code_type">
<option value="bb_deck">BB-Code with DECK tags (for MTG-Forum.de)</option>
<option value="bb_url">BB-Code with URL tags (recommended for most forums)</option>
<option value="markdown">Markdown List (for reddit)</option>
<option value="markdown_table">Markdown Table (for reddit)</option>
<option value="html_wide">HTML code for high table</option>

</select>

<script type="text/javascript">
			function generate_code_action(e) {
				e.preventDefault();

				document.location.href = 'https://deckstats.net/decks/117406/1237928-anafenza/en?get_code=1' +
					'&code_type=' + $('#code_type').val() +
					'&code_extended=' + $('#code_extended').val() +
					'&code_html_nl=' + ($('#code_html_nl').is(':checked')? 'on' : 'off');
			}

			$(function(){
				$('#get_code').click(generate_code_action);

				$('#code_type,#code_extended,#code_html_nl').change(function(e) {
					$('#code_result').hide();
				});
				$('#code_type').change(function(e) {
					if($(this).val().substr(0, 4) == 'html') {
						$('#code_html_nl_label').show();
					} else {
						$('#code_html_nl_label').hide();
					}
				});
				updateCodeType($('#code_type')[0]);
			});
		</script>

var LNG = "en";
var COUNTRY = "DK";

//as a function so it can be called when async loading of cardlink is done
function nk_cardlink_init() {
	nk_deckstats_lng = LNG;
	
	//https://hacks.mozilla.org/2009/07/cross-site-xmlhttprequest-with-cors/
	try {
		if (COUNTRY != 'PL' && 'withCredentials' in new XMLHttpRequest()) {
			nk_cardlink_external = 'https://www.mtg-forum.de/db/get.php';
		} else {
			nk_cardlink_external = PATH+'/db_tunnel.php';
		}
	} catch(ex) {
		//this catches IE8, which may not allow 'new XMLHttpRequest()'
		nk_cardlink_external = PATH+'/db_tunnel.php';
	}
		
	
	nk_cardlink_lng = (nk_deckstats_lng == 'de'? 'de' : 'en');
	nk_use_mana_sprites = true;
	nk_cardlink_all = true;
};

<div id="deck_tabs-tools">
<div class="section_header" id="deck_code_header">Embed Into Forums or Website</div>
<div class="inhalt2">
<div style="margin-bottom: 5px;">
For forums and blogs please select one of the BB-Code options. For websites and forums that support HTML (e.g. Wizards Community Forums) you can use the HTML options!	</div>
<div style="margin-top: 1em;">
<div>
<select name="code_type" id="code_type">
<option value="bb_deck">BB-Code with DECK tags (for MTG-Forum.de)</option>
<option value="bb_url">BB-Code with URL tags (recommended for most forums)</option>
<option value="markdown">Markdown List (for reddit)</option>
<option value="markdown_table">Markdown Table (for reddit)</option>
<option value="html_wide">HTML code for high table</option>
<option value="html_normal">HTML for wide table (recommended for Wizards Community)</option>
</select>
<select name="code_extended" id="code_extended">
<option value="0">Normal View</option>
<option value="1">Extended View (with mana symbols)</option>
</select>
<input class="button" type="submit" name="get_code" id="get_code" value="Generate Embed Code" />
</div>
<div>
<label id="code_html_nl_label">
<input name="code_html_nl" id="code_html_nl" type="checkbox" style="border: 0" />
Use linebreaks in HTML code (disable for Wizards Community) </label>
</div>
<script type="text/javascript">
			function generate_code_action(e) {
				e.preventDefault();

				document.location.href = 'https://deckstats.net/decks/120512/1238514-for-rose/en?get_code=1' +
					'&code_type=' + $('#code_type').val() +
					'&code_extended=' + $('#code_extended').val() +
					'&code_html_nl=' + ($('#code_html_nl').is(':checked')? 'on' : 'off');
			}

			$(function(){
				$('#get_code').click(generate_code_action);

				$('#code_type,#code_extended,#code_html_nl').change(function(e) {
					$('#code_result').hide();
				});
				$('#code_type').change(function(e) {
					if($(this).val().substr(0, 4) == 'html') {
						$('#code_html_nl_label').show();
					} else {
						$('#code_html_nl_label').hide();
					}
				});
				updateCodeType($('#code_type')[0]);
			});
		</script>
</div>
</div>

<div id="deck_tabs-edh">
<div class="inhalt2">
With this tool you can get recommendations for new cards to add to your EDH deck, based on which cards other players play with this Commander.	To make sure your deck is analyzed properly, please <b>flag your Commander in the deckbuilder</b> or put it in a separate section called "Commander"!</div>
<div id="edh_specify_commander">
<h3 class="section_header">Specify Commander</h3>
<div class="inhalt2">
<div>
Unfortunately, we could not automatically detect the commander in this deck. Please choose it here: </div>

function nk_cardlink_init() {
	nk_deckstats_lng = LNG;
	
	//https://hacks.mozilla.org/2009/07/cross-site-xmlhttprequest-with-cors/
	try {
		if (COUNTRY != 'PL' && 'withCredentials' in new XMLHttpRequest()) {

		//this catches IE8, which may not allow 'new XMLHttpRequest()'

	}

<div class="any_dialog" id="download_regsheet_dialog" title="Download Deck Sheet">
<p>
To play your deck at an official ("DCI-sanctioned") tournament you need a deck registration sheet. Here you can download such a sheet pre-filled with the cards in this deck!	</p>
<div style="margin-top: .5em">
<label for="download_regsheet_sort">Sort cards by:</label>
<select id="download_regsheet_sort" class="ui-corner-all">
<option value="name">Card Name</option>
<option value="amount">Amount</option>
<option value="type">Type</option>
<option value="none">do not sort</option>
</select>
</div>
<div style="margin-top: .5em">
<label>
<input type="checkbox" checked="checked" id="download_regsheet_dci_details">
Include my DCI number and name </label>
(-&gt;
<a href="https://deckstats.net/settings/?lng=en" target="_blank">
Your Settings</a>)
</div>
<p>
<i>
Please note: This is not an official DCI service. So please always make extra sure that the sheet contains all the cards in your deck and fulfils all DCI requirements. If you notice anything wrong, please let us know! DCI is a trademark of of Wizards of the Coast LLC.
</i>
</p>

<div id="deck_overview_info">
<h3>
Description </h3>
<div class="deck_overview_section_content deck_overview_info_description deck_text_editable_container" data-decktextfield="description">
<div>
<div>
This is a 5-colored token deck.<br />
<br />
- Green and white dominates the color pie here.<br />
- Populate as much as you can and use it to draw, <a href="https://www.mtg-forum.de/db/magiccard.php?utf8=1&amp;lng=en&amp;card=Drain+Life" target="_blank" class="cardlink_auto">drain life</a>, gain mana, or burn your opponents out!<br />
- Many &quot;creatures you control&quot; do rely on you having creatures - <a href="https://www.mtg-forum.de/db/magiccard.php?utf8=1&amp;lng=en&amp;card=Duh" target="_blank" class="cardlink_auto">duh</a>.<br />
- <a href="https://www.mtg-forum.de/db/magiccard.php?utf8=1&amp;lng=en&amp;card=Settle+the+Wreckage" target="_blank" class="cardlink_auto">Settle the Wreckage</a> is a great way to mana ramp - just FYI - if used on your own attacking tokens, like who cares you exiled 5 of your 0/1 <a href="https://www.mtg-forum.de/db/magiccard.php?utf8=1&amp;lng=en&amp;card=Plant" target="_blank" class="cardlink_auto">plant</a> or eldrazi tokens but you get 5 basic lands into play tapped :) </div>
</div>
</div>

<div id="deck_tabs-tools">
<div class="section_header" id="deck_code_header">Embed Into Forums or Website</div>
<div class="inhalt2">
<div style="margin-bottom: 5px;">
For forums and blogs please select one of the BB-Code options. For websites and forums that support HTML (e.g. Wizards Community Forums) you can use the HTML options!	</div>
<div style="margin-top: 1em;">
<div>
<select name="code_type" id="code_type">
<option value="bb_deck">BB-Code with DECK tags (for MTG-Forum.de)</option>
<option value="bb_url">BB-Code with URL tags (recommended for most forums)</option>
<option value="markdown">Markdown List (for reddit)</option>
<option value="markdown_table">Markdown Table (for reddit)</option>
<option value="html_wide">HTML code for high table</option>
<option value="html_normal">HTML for wide table (recommended for Wizards Community)</option>
</select>
<select name="code_extended" id="code_extended">
<option value="0">Normal View</option>
<option value="1">Extended View (with mana symbols)</option>
</select>
<input class="button" type="submit" name="get_code" id="get_code" value="Generate Embed Code" />
</div>
<div>
<label id="code_html_nl_label">
<input name="code_html_nl" id="code_html_nl" type="checkbox" style="border: 0" />
Use linebreaks in HTML code (disable for Wizards Community) </label>
</div>
<script type="text/javascript">
			function generate_code_action(e) {
				e.preventDefault();

				document.location.href = 'https://deckstats.net/decks/124288/1238297-sliver-queen-brood-queen-of-to/en?get_code=1' +
					'&code_type=' + $('#code_type').val() +
					'&code_extended=' + $('#code_extended').val() +
					'&code_html_nl=' + ($('#code_html_nl').is(':checked')? 'on' : 'off');
			}

			$(function(){
				$('#get_code').click(generate_code_action);

				$('#code_type,#code_extended,#code_html_nl').change(function(e) {
					$('#code_result').hide();
				});
				$('#code_type').change(function(e) {
					if($(this).val().substr(0, 4) == 'html') {
						$('#code_html_nl_label').show();
					} else {
						$('#code_html_nl_label').hide();
					}
				});
				updateCodeType($('#code_type')[0]);
			});
		</script>
</div>
</div>

With this tool you can get recommendations for new cards to add to your EDH deck, based on which cards other players play with this Commander.	To make sure your deck is analyzed properly, please <b>flag your Commander in the deckbuilder</b> or put it in a separate section called "Commander"!</div>

	nk_deckstats_lng = LNG;
	
	//https://hacks.mozilla.org/2009/07/cross-site-xmlhttprequest-with-cors/
	try {
		if (COUNTRY != 'PL' && 'withCredentials' in new XMLHttpRequest()) {

<input id="download_deck_include_comments" checked="checked" type="checkbox">
Include card comments (.dec)
</label>
</p>
</div>
<div class="any_dialog" id="download_regsheet_dialog" title="Download Deck Sheet">
<p>
To play your deck at an official ("DCI-sanctioned") tournament you need a deck registration sheet. Here you can download such a sheet pre-filled with the cards in this deck!	</p>
<div style="margin-top: .5em">
<label for="download_regsheet_sort">Sort cards by:</label>
<select id="download_regsheet_sort" class="ui-corner-all">
<option value="name">Card Name</option>
<option value="amount">Amount</option>
<option value="type">Type</option>
<option value="none">do not sort</option>
</select>
</div>
<div style="margin-top: .5em">
<label>
<input type="checkbox" checked="checked" id="download_regsheet_dci_details">
Include my DCI number and name </label>
(-&gt;
<a href="https://deckstats.net/settings/?lng=en" target="_blank">
Your Settings</a>)
</div>
<p>
<i>
Please note: This is not an official DCI service. So please always make extra sure that the sheet contains all the cards in your deck and fulfils all DCI requirements. If you notice anything wrong, please let us know! DCI is a trademark of of Wizards of the Coast LLC.
</i>
</p>
</div>
<div class="any_dialog" id="deck_columns_dialog" title="Select columns">

<div id="deck_tabs-tools">
<div class="section_header" id="deck_code_header">Embed Into Forums or Website</div>
<div class="inhalt2">
<div style="margin-bottom: 5px;">
For forums and blogs please select one of the BB-Code options. For websites and forums that support HTML (e.g. Wizards Community Forums) you can use the HTML options!	</div>
<div style="margin-top: 1em;">
<div>
<select name="code_type" id="code_type">
<option value="bb_deck">BB-Code with DECK tags (for MTG-Forum.de)</option>
<option value="bb_url">BB-Code with URL tags (recommended for most forums)</option>
<option value="markdown">Markdown List (for reddit)</option>
<option value="markdown_table">Markdown Table (for reddit)</option>
<option value="html_wide">HTML code for high table</option>
<option value="html_normal">HTML for wide table (recommended for Wizards Community)</option>
</select>
<select name="code_extended" id="code_extended">
<option value="0">Normal View</option>
<option value="1">Extended View (with mana symbols)</option>
</select>
<input class="button" type="submit" name="get_code" id="get_code" value="Generate Embed Code" />
</div>
<div>
<label id="code_html_nl_label">
<input name="code_html_nl" id="code_html_nl" type="checkbox" style="border: 0" />
Use linebreaks in HTML code (disable for Wizards Community) </label>
</div>
<script type="text/javascript">
			function generate_code_action(e) {
				e.preventDefault();

				document.location.href = 'https://deckstats.net/decks/95652/1224559-alesha-/en?get_code=1' +
					'&code_type=' + $('#code_type').val() +
					'&code_extended=' + $('#code_extended').val() +
					'&code_html_nl=' + ($('#code_html_nl').is(':checked')? 'on' : 'off');
			}

			$(function(){
				$('#get_code').click(generate_code_action);

				$('#code_type,#code_extended,#code_html_nl').change(function(e) {
					$('#code_result').hide();
				});
				$('#code_type').change(function(e) {
					if($(this).val().substr(0, 4) == 'html') {
						$('#code_html_nl_label').show();
					} else {
						$('#code_html_nl_label').hide();
					}
				});
				updateCodeType($('#code_type')[0]);
			});
		</script>
</div>
</div>

With this tool you can get recommendations for new cards to add to your EDH deck, based on which cards other players play with this Commander.	To make sure your deck is analyzed properly, please <b>flag your Commander in the deckbuilder</b> or put it in a separate section called "Commander"!</div>

<script>
var PATH = "\/\/deckstats.net";
var LNG = "en";
var COUNTRY = "DK";
var user_logged_in = false;

//as a function so it can be called when async loading of cardlink is done
function nk_cardlink_init() {
	nk_deckstats_lng = LNG;
	
	//https://hacks.mozilla.org/2009/07/cross-site-xmlhttprequest-with-cors/
	try {
		if (COUNTRY != 'PL' && 'withCredentials' in new XMLHttpRequest()) {
			nk_cardlink_external = 'https://www.mtg-forum.de/db/get.php';
		} else {
			nk_cardlink_external = PATH+'/db_tunnel.php';
		}
	} catch(ex) {
		//this catches IE8, which may not allow 'new XMLHttpRequest()'
		nk_cardlink_external = PATH+'/db_tunnel.php';
	}
		
	
	nk_cardlink_lng = (nk_deckstats_lng == 'de'? 'de' : 'en');
	nk_use_mana_sprites = true;
	nk_cardlink_all = true;
};

nk_cardlink_init();

	//SMF data
	smf_user_id = 0;	
	smf_user_name = "Guest";
	//for session validation in comments
	smf_session_var = "f5c6f06c";
	smf_session_id = "a793911c407bba833a62d1c39e40ed1a";

</script> <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />

<script>
var PATH = "\/\/deckstats.net";
var LNG = "en";
var COUNTRY = "DK";
var user_logged_in = false;

//as a function so it can be called when async loading of cardlink is done
function nk_cardlink_init() {
	nk_deckstats_lng = LNG;
	
	//https://hacks.mozilla.org/2009/07/cross-site-xmlhttprequest-with-cors/
	try {
		if (COUNTRY != 'PL' && 'withCredentials' in new XMLHttpRequest()) {
			nk_cardlink_external = 'https://www.mtg-forum.de/db/get.php';
		} else {
			nk_cardlink_external = PATH+'/db_tunnel.php';
		}
	} catch(ex) {
		//this catches IE8, which may not allow 'new XMLHttpRequest()'
		nk_cardlink_external = PATH+'/db_tunnel.php';
	}
		
	
	nk_cardlink_lng = (nk_deckstats_lng == 'de'? 'de' : 'en');
	nk_use_mana_sprites = true;
	nk_cardlink_all = true;
};

nk_cardlink_init();

	//SMF data
	smf_user_id = 0;	
	smf_user_name = "Guest";
	//for session validation in comments
	smf_session_var = "f19821e";
	smf_session_id = "afadef9c9dc357b1b79abe0aa2afc639";

</script> <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
